Package ProjectRegistration

Class ProjectRegistration

java.lang.Object
ProjectRegistration.ProjectRegistration
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntity
public class ProjectRegistration extends Object implements IEntity
Represents a project registration record where an officer registers to handle a BTO project. Implements IEntity for standardized CSV persistence.
